    "Page 35 of 39 32",
    "The fifth requirement is related to the generation of explanations (R5).",
    "The approaches found for explainability can be implemented at two levels:",
    "• At the level of weights (R5a): This simple method creates visual descriptions regarding the weight values of the network.",
    "While simple, it is also restricted since the main information is only the strongness of the relationships between tokens."
